      "text": "The pow-er of Thy Mar--tyrs, O my__ Christ,__ is ver---y great, who drive off e---vil spir---its al-though__ they lie__ in sep--ul----chres;__ by the__ faith of__ God the Trin-i-ty,____ they__ van---quished__ the ad-ver--sar--y’s pow---er__ when__ they con--tend------ed for the sake of true___ re-li-gion.__"
